<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>The Chiv Hunt | Song Qingzhao Zhufu</title>
  <meta name="description" content="The Chiv Hunt — a record of fights, lessons, and growth on the path of learning." />
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#0a0c0b;
      --panel:#151b18;
      --panel-2:#1b231f;
      --line:rgba(180,190,185,0.18);
      --jade:#3f8f68;
      --jade-bright:#6dc89a;
      --silver:#c0c7c4;
      --silver-soft:#98a39d;
      --ink:#e6ece8;
      --shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
      --radius:20px;
      --max:900px;
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(63,143,104,0.18), transparent 35%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0c0b 0%, #0d1110 40%, #090a09 100%);
      color:var(--ink);
      line-height:1.7;
    }

    a{color:var(--jade-bright);text-decoration:none}
    a:hover{color:#8ce0b2}

    .wrap{
      width:min(var(--max), calc(100% - 2rem));
      margin:0 auto;
    }

    .top{
      padding:3rem 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(21,27,24,0.96), rgba(15,20,18,0.92));
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      padding:2rem;
    }

    .eyebrow{
      display:inline-block;
      padding:0.35rem 0.7rem;
      border:1px solid rgba(109,200,154,0.25);
      border-radius:999px;
      color:var(--jade-bright);
      background:rgba(63,143,104,0.08);
      font-size:0.82rem;
      letter-spacing:0.08em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      margin-bottom:1rem;
    }

    h1,h2,h3{
      line-height:1.15;
      margin:0 0 0.8rem;
    }

    h1{
      font-size:clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 4rem);
      color:#fff;
    }

    h2{
      color:var(--jade-bright);
      margin-top:2rem;
    }

    h3{
      color:#fff;
      margin-top:1.5rem;
    }

    p{
      margin:0 0 1rem;
      color:#dbe3de;
    }

    .lead{
      font-size:1.1rem;
      color:var(--silver);
      max-width:42rem;
    }

    .panel{
      margin-top:1.25rem;
      padding:1.25rem;
      border-radius:16px;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(27,35,31,0.96), rgba(16,21,19,0.96));
      border:1px solid var(--line);
    }

    ul{
      padding-left:1.2rem;
    }

    li{
      margin:0.35rem 0;
    }

    .timeline-group{
      margin-top:1rem;
      padding-top:0.25rem;
      border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .note{
      margin-top:1.5rem;
      padding:1rem 1.1rem;
      border-left:3px solid var(--jade);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      font-style:italic;
      color:#edf5f0;
    }

    .footer{
      padding:2rem 0 3rem;
      color:var(--silver-soft);
      font-size:0.95rem;
    }

    .btn{
      display:inline-block;
      margin-top:1rem;
      padding:0.8rem 1rem;
      border-radius:999px;
      font-weight:700;
      border:1px solid rgba(109,200,154,0.3);
      background:rgba(63,143,104,0.1);
      color:#f2faf5;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="top">
    <div class="wrap">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="eyebrow">Song Qingzhao Zhufu</div>
        <h1>The Chiv Hunt</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          A personal record of fighting members of the Order of Chivalry. Each signature represents a fight, a lesson, and a step along the path of learning.
        </p>

        <div class="panel">
          <h2>Hunt Stats</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Knights fought: 47</li>
            <li>Events visited: 18</li>
            <li>Kingdoms fought in: 3</li>
            <li>Years active: 2023–Present</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="panel">
          <h2>Signature Timeline</h2>

          <div class="timeline-group">
            <h3>2025</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Sir Ulrich von Brandenburg — Gulf Wars</li>
              <li>Sir ___ — Pennsic</li>
              <li>Sir ___ — Silver Hammer</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-group">
            <h3>2024</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Sir ___ — War of the Wings</li>
              <li>Sir ___ — Castle Wars</li>
              <li>Sir ___ — Yule Toy</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-group">
            <h3>2023</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Sir ___ — Silver Hammer</li>
              <li>Sir ___ — Meridian Grand Tournament</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel">
          <h2>Lessons Learned</h2>

          <p><strong>Sir Ulrich von Brandenburg</strong><br>
          Lesson: Control the distance before committing to a strike.</p>

          <p><strong>Sir ___</strong><br>
          Lesson: Footwork wins fights before the sword moves.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="note">
          The Chiv Hunt is not just a list of names. It is a record of growth, humility, and the lessons earned one fight at a time.
        </div>

        <a class="btn" href="https://www.facebook.com/share/1AhxAaLQzQ/?" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Follow on Facebook</a>
      </section>

      <div class="footer">
        Song Qingzhao Zhufu • #SongStrong • #GreenKid
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>